data.description: THIS RANCH HOME IS A MUST SEE!  Located in highly sought Monroe school district! Beautiful Farmhouse plan with large rocking-chair porch, spacious open concept, courtyard entrance, breakfast bar+ eat in kichen area, formal dining room, and Customized, separate garage.  ADDED VALUE -The square footage does not take into account the enclosed garage area on the main structure.  Home has renovated kitchen, owners' bath, and Custom/Dual level, back deck.  The Primary Suite Includes 2 large walk-in closets. Primary bath includes double vanity, granite counters and Tile shower with shower glass door. Over 1 acre of land!  USDA 100% approved.
